{"id":316718,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/10/维权网-学生右派罗开文乞讨被打，市区两级不公/","date":"2013-10-06T17:34:01Z","modified":"2013-10-06T17:34:01Z","title":"维权网 | 学生右派罗开文乞讨被打，市区两级不公开政府信息遭诉","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"><span></span><span></span><br /><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span><span> </span></span><span>（维权网信息员李岩报道）据罗开文向本网信息员透露：</span>2013</span></span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>8</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>29</span></span><span>日中午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>12</span></span><span>点</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>20</span></span><span>左右，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>76</span></span><span>岁的落魄钟表行老板、学生右派“活化石”罗开文穿着乞讨衣服，在小南街寻找在“乞讨”过程中遇到的好心人，被一辆</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>110</span></span><span>警车下来人将其带到汪家拐派出所，为出示任何合法手续，也没有告知其违反了什么法律规定。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span><br /><span> </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span></span></span><br /><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2013</span></span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>9</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2</span></span><span>日，罗开文展开了一系列维权行动，他先向青羊区政府申请行政复议，要求确认警察限制他自由的行为违法。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span><br /><span> </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span></span></span><br /><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>9</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>3</span></span><span>日，为了取得证据，通过特快专递，向成都市公安局申请政府信息公开，要求其公开</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>110</span></span><span>报警记录和处警记录，同时，向青羊区公安分局申请政府信息公开，要求公开派出所的监控录像，和限制他自由的执法依据。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span><br /><span> </span><span></span><br /><span>截止</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2013</span></span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>6</span></span><span>日，成都市公安局没有对他的信息公开作出任何回复，罗开文表示：将依法向成都市中级人民法院提起行政诉讼。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span><br /><span> </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span></span></span><br /><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>9</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>16</span></span><span>日，青羊区公安分局对他的信息公开作出答复，同意他去汪家拐派出所查看监控录像，但不许他复制录像，对于他要求的执法依据，则以不属于信息公开内容为由不予公开。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span><br /><span></span><span></span><br /><span>对此，罗开文先生表示：他将对青羊区公安分局的信息公开答复提起行政诉讼，用法律来维护自己的合法权益。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span><br /><span> </span><span><span></span></span><br /><span><span>罗开文先生称：向青羊区政府申请的行政复议已经受理，目前正等待复议结果。</span></span></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-aNzE1NPllzE/UlF_-t1QPAI/AAAAAAAApGQ/DpCQmLmRsqk/s1600/QQ%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20131006231219.png\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"400\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-aNzE1NPllzE/UlF_-t1QPAI/AAAAAAAApGQ/DpCQmLmRsqk/s400/QQ%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20131006231219.png\" width=\"281\" /></a></div>\n<p><span><span></span></span><br /><span><span></span></span><br /><span><span></span></span> </div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}